OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney says time before
OL,4,CBeatles were famous gave the group
OL,5,Cstrength
OL,7,FSir Paul McCartney has said the time
OL,8,Fspent together before The Beatles rose
OL,9,Fto fame is what gave the group "its
OL,10,Fstrength".
OL,12,FThe singer-songwriter, 83, discussed
OL,13,Fthe journey behind making his latest
OL,14,Falbum, The Boys Of Dungeon Lane, which
OL,15,Frecounts a collection of memories from
OL,16,Fhis formative years, during a special
OL,17,Fevent in London.
OL,26,@qD@`OUrD@IO]
