OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781205078
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney says time before
OL,4,CBeatles were famous gave the group
OL,5,Cstrength
OL,7,FHosted by comedian Rob Brydon at the
OL,8,FRoundhouse, a multi-arts venue and
OL,9,Fyouth charity in Camden, the album was
OL,10,Fplayed in full and split up with
OL,11,Freflections, anecdotes, and the
OL,12,Foccasional strum of a guitar by Sir
OL,13,FPaul himself.
OL,15,FFans filled the music and arts venue
OL,16,Ffor the sold-out event where the
OL,17,Fmusician shared his song-writing
OL,18,Fprocess, opening up about how he often
OL,19,Fhas "no idea" what he is doing - and
OL,20,Fproudly so.
OL,26,@{D@EOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781205078
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney says time before
OL,4,CBeatles were famous gave the group
OL,5,Cstrength
OL,7,F"I don't want to know any rules
OL,8,Fbecause that's the fun of it," he said.
OL,10,FSir Paul added that he has a "hard
OL,11,Ftime doing down songs" because "it's
OL,12,Fjust not me".
OL,14,F"Positive songs I really like. If I've
OL,15,Fgot a down song, I'll suddenly try and
OL,16,Flift it, give it a happy ending or
OL,17,Fsomething," he said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@^O]rD@^OUsD@VO]sD@`OUtD@LO]vD@
OL,26,AAOUyD@KO]
