PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781205078
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney says time before
OL,4,CBeatles were famous gave the group
OL,5,Cstrength
OL,7,FHe said: "We had some great times
OL,8,Ftogether.
OL,10,F"Besides, this was all before The
OL,11,FBeatles, so this really gave The
OL,12,FBeatles its strength.
OL,14,F"We knew each other really well."
OL,16,FReflecting on the success of the band,
OL,17,FSir Paul said: "I can look back on it
OL,18,Fnow like I'm a major fan.
OL,26,@oD@JOUrD@AOUvD@AOUvD@aO]yD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
