OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781205078
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney says time before
OL,4,CBeatles were famous gave the group
OL,5,Cstrength
OL,7,F"When you're doing it, you've got to
OL,8,Fbe a bit modest. But once it's all
OL,9,Fdone, you don't have to be modest at
OL,10,Fall!
OL,12,F"So I do enjoy looking back on those
OL,13,Fmemories."
OL,15,FThe album features a duet with Sir
OL,16,FRingo Starr titled Home To Us, which
OL,17,Fhe revealed "came about by chance"
OL,18,Fafter the pair were separately working
OL,19,Fwith the same producer, Andrew Watt.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUuD@JO]yD@MOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
