OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781205078
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney says time before
OL,4,CBeatles were famous gave the group
OL,5,Cstrength
OL,7,FIt is the first duet the two have made
OL,8,Ftogether with Sir Paul adding that at
OL,9,Ffirst he thought the drummer hated it.
OL,11,FThe 14-track record was named after a
OL,12,Fplace close to his childhood home in
OL,13,FForthlin Road in Speke, Liverpool.
OL,15,FReleased at the end of May, the record
OL,16,Fwas Sir Paul's first album in five
OL,17,Fyears and climbed to number one on the
OL,18,FUK album charts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
